  "title": "助记媒介的实例",
  "content": "<ul><li data-pid=\"VhYEecCQ\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//quantum.country/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">量子国度</a>》<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"ZtvBaxhc\"> 使用 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z72ioKyd4X48WndtAsfkhnKwsD8o5PaaT384o\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Orbit</a> 编写：<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"3K8UKPnE\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//andymatuschak.org/prompts/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">如何写好出好卡片</a><sup data-text=\"如何写出好卡片：利用间隔重复创造理解\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/434074509\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>》作者：Andy Matuschak<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"li640CnC\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//metarationality.com/maps-and-territory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">地图，领土和元理性</a>》作者：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z29Uv6CnK2xSy3nivekQwMMXW2jwzd4yQWbN\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">David Chapman</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"R8AeBhnk\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//nintil.com/age-and-science/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">普朗克是对的吗？衰老对科学家生产力的影响</a>》作者：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zAxicVEnF4ZKani8m5LXHYRDDvrZctBvWYV\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Jose Luis Ricon Fernandez de la Puente</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"K4A-IPKT\"> （XXX 的本科微观经济学课程，私有）<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"v1ZbTfxj\"> （XXX 本科线性电路理论课程，私有）<br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"BEfZvi4c\"> 基于别人建立的系统：<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"PpW6bDCe\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//dawnguide.com/home\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">曙光指南</a>》作者：Mispy（定制实现）<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"u5y_-3Zy\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zzfor7LXCY9JBRjFmMaeLw5zV69GM2dSDQA\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Soren Bjornstad</a> 即将出版的 TiddlyWiki 图书（以 TiddlyWiki 为中心的新实现）<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"vcBdieIR\"> 《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zBM4qbJhN1XA4wBpDCj2fonXiz4sgQFe4YR\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Think Saver</a>》<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"7zs1kvpM\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.lesswrong.com/posts/JgBBuDf5uZHmpEMDs/how-you-can-gain-self-control-without-self-control\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">lesswrong.com/posts/JgB</span><span class=\"invisible\">BuDf5uZHmpEMDs/how-you-can-gain-self-control-without-self-control</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a> </li></ul></ul></ul><h3>更远的地方</h3><p data-pid=\"a_Cx2XGp\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2LGZ8cXBcQMP7YuAHbeVyCSLZoiMXvQNKCok\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Execute Program</a> 与此有关，因为它也是一个带有嵌入间隔重复功能的交流媒介的例子，但是它与其他媒介之间的区别要比其他媒介之间的区别大得多。</p><p data-pid=\"1o5dz50o\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z8MgFD7B7QRqqGZXsJqeGpm5PJhroPwb6BW2V\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Chessable MoveTrainer</a> 同样是一种集成的教学媒介和间隔重复系统，改编自国际象棋训练文本。</p><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"n0TvMWFV\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/459483765\" class=\"internal\">助记媒介（Mnemonic medium）</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"tK_Q4Oar\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/fd3642075287be95e5f5d0eafbf1ac8c\" data-hash=\"fd3642075287be95e5f5d0eafbf1ac8c\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$fd3642075287be95e5f5d0eafbf1ac8c\">@changxv</a> <br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zDmYvwSyN9YRv5HgDYwX19C28jC9qZ5qiMJ\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Substantive examples of the mnemonic medium (andymatuschak.org)</a></blockquote>",
